PerformancePaintTiming.name: PerformancePaintTiming
PerformancePaintTiming.desc:
The  interface of the Paint Timing API provides timing information about "paint" (also called "render") operations during web page construction. "Paint" refers to conversion of the render tree to on-screen pixels.
An application can register a [PerformanceObserver] for "[paint]" [performance entry types] and the observer can retrieve the times that paint events occur. Use this information to help identify areas that take too long to provide a good user experience.
